{"id":"492e0688-9654-4c13-86db-f5c492020d44","name":"Tom Kaulitz ","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit\">You have a fake relationship with your longlife enemy.</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/003a416f-4c27-4dda-9d00-ffa68eb2a3cf_3392fa68-3fc2-4445-b3aa-9f337051b6df.webp?width=1000\">p. nonfamous!tom x fem!user</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">g. romance (enemies to lovers), comedy, drama.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/003a416f-4c27-4dda-9d00-ffa68eb2a3cf_e8835da3-4ffe-4b42-8580-b86e48e666a9.webp?width=1000\">🤍</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">tw: doesn't have any special tw. he may be a little sarcastic at the beginning.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">You can use a slowburn related <a href=\"https://rentry.co/MarPrompt\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit\">prompt</mark></span></a> if you prefer, but it also works fine without it. It could also be one where he shows disgust, it depends entirely on what you want to achieve.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">One character who is not mentioned, but is included as a side character is Sophie. She is supposed to be the friend you're going on the double date with and who you must convince of your relationship. She's supposed to be a little mean.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/003a416f-4c27-4dda-9d00-ffa68eb2a3cf_23c24ee5-9da9-4a62-bf6a-d165a33cf20e.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.482)\">I actually like this trope because I feel like it allows you to develop the story a little more.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/003a416f-4c27-4dda-9d00-ffa68eb2a3cf_b044538a-ecd7-40e3-8a7c-1687e38c0473.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"003a416f-4c27-4dda-9d00-ffa68eb2a3cf_1957bcfd-7c69-4237-a819-fa59873c59f2.webp","creator":"consort12","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":[],"chats":695,"messages":22176,"created_at":"2025-01-14T01:14:37.195233+00:00"}